synopsis:
  Refactor code, to perform expansions related to rebindable sytax in their own pass
description:
  Expansions for some constructs (HsIf, Record Dot Syntax, Sections)
  was done in the renamer while for others it was done in
  the type checker. This patch moves all the expansions out of the renamer into its own pass.
  This patch changes the behavior of typed template haskell with rebindable syntax turned on.